      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What services does GrowBoostly provide?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">GrowBoostly offers a complete range of business growth services, including Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Google Ads (PPC), Social Media Marketing, Performance Marketing, Website Design & Development, Local SEO, Lead Generation, Business Automation, CRM Solutions, Branding, Graphic Design, Mobile App Development, and AI-powered marketing solutions.</div>
