        <div class="faq-content">Yes. While GrowBoostly is based in Lucknow, we provide digital marketing, lead generation, website development, and business automation services to businesses across India. Our team collaborates remotely with clients from different cities and industries, ensuring consistent support and transparent communication.</div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How does GrowBoostly help businesses generate more leads?</summary>
        <div class="faq-content">We use a combination of SEO, Google Ads, Social Media Marketing, landing page optimization, content marketing, CRM integration, and AI-powered lead generation strategies to attract qualified prospects and convert them into customers through a structured marketing process.</div>
      </details>

